
*--------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*                    S C E N A R I O   H E A D E R
*
* filename - res_cfg.s
*
* $Revision$
*
* $Date$
*
*		Test of the RESET CONFIG feature
*
*		Loop test
*
*		Configuration:
*		-------------
*		RESET_CONFIG compile option MUST be turned ON
*		One bundle with 1 or 2 member links required as a minimum
*
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------*

*
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Set simulation flags
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
*

	F	1	1	1

*
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Start simulation
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
*

	G
*
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Reset of the Loop counters
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
*

	Z

*
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Loop Testing of STOP_RQ/RESET_RQ/SET_CONFIG_RQ
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
*

	{	50

*
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Stop the Network Access
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
*

		B	z	0	F
*
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Reset the Network Access Configuration
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
*

		B	z	0	D

*
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Send Configuration Buffer (Member Links Configuration)
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
*


		B	z	255	C	MPPP_CFG_TYPE_MEMBER_LINK
*
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Send Configuration Buffer (Bundle Configuration)
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
*


		B	z	255	C	B
*
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Display Loop Counters
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
*

		D

	}
*
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Terminate the simulation
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
*

	Q
